description:
Past and present collide in a time-splitting adventure! Shadow the Hedgehog, in a frantic chase for truth and understanding, is haunted by memories of battles fought and lives lost. But these nightmares aren't just lingering pain... they're prompted by a force Shadow thought was long destroyed...

Continue the story in SONIC X SHADOW GENERATIONS, arriving October 25th!
title: SONIC X SHADOW GENERATIONS: Dark Beginnings Full Animation (With Bonus Ending) | Story Trailer

description:
As the Switch approaches the end of its lifecycle, Super Mario Party Jamboree attempts to find the sweet spot between its two predecessors and stumbles into an issue of quantity over quality in the process.

#SuperMarioPartyJamboree #Review #GameSpot
title: Super Mario Party Jamboree Review | This Party Is Too Crowded
